com.ibm.team.scm.common

Class IRepositoryProgressMonitor.RepositoryMonitorFactory

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.ibm.team.scm.common.IRepositoryProgressMonitor.RepositoryMonitorFactory
  • Enclosing interface:
    IRepositoryProgressMonitor

    public static class IRepositoryProgressMonitor.RepositoryMonitorFactory
extends java.lang.Object
    A helper factory for creating repository monitors. It's recommended that when calling a service method from the client with an existing IProgressMonitor that the repository monitor be created and initialized to wrap the client side monitor as follows: IRepositoryProgressMonitor repoMonitor = IRepositoryProgressMonitor.ITEM_FACTORY. createItem(monitor); serviceInterface.doIt(repoMonitor);
